---

<Layout
	title="About Voice Lab Weekly"
	description="Independent, hands-on coverage of ElevenLabs — the leading AI voice, music, and audio platform."
	pubDate={new Date('April 18 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Voice Lab Weekly is an independent publication that covers ElevenLabs — the AI platform behind some of the most natural-sounding synthetic voices, fastest transcription models, and most expressive generative music on the internet.
	</p>

	<p>
		We exist for one reason: the ElevenLabs product suite keeps expanding faster than any single launch post can keep up with. Text-to-speech, voice cloning, voice design, dubbing, sound effects, music, and a full conversational agents platform — each of these is a serious tool in its own right, and most creators never discover half of what's available inside a single account.
	</p>

	<h2>What we publish</h2>
	<p>
		Three short, practical posts every day. Tutorials when a new model ships. Comparisons when a new feature replaces an old one. Creative experiments when something genuinely surprising is possible. Every post is written to be usable — if you can't open a tab and try the thing yourself after reading it, we didn't do our job.
	</p>

	<h2>How we stay independent</h2>
	<p>
		This site is reader-supported via affiliate links. When you click through to ElevenLabs from one of our posts and sign up, we earn a small commission — at no cost to you. That's it. No sponsorships, no paid placement, no gated content.
	</p>

	<p>
		Got a tutorial request, a correction, or a use case you'd like us to cover? Find us on the links in the footer.
	</p>
</Layout>
